channel.title: Leaving
channel.description:
This may be my [i]last[/i] thread created here at Moparscape. I've made my decision, I'm quitting. Taharok, you can have that party you've always wanted. Anyway, I'd like to thank a few of my friends here at moparscape. Let's start..
O M G(Dakota) - Although you lied to me about dying, You we're a good friend. HcoJustin (Justin) - You were a great friend. Fat cookies - <3 Klorox(Devin) - You're fucking awesome, nuff said. Pie`(wut) - Easy to talk to, you makez lewk lulz. AMERIKA(Don't know if I should be releasing his name) - You're fucking great man. Easy to talk to, we always got along. Taharok - Although most of the time you were an ass, It's fine, It was for a reason. You've taught me a lot from that. Silabsoft - I enjoy your Randomized blocks!!1oneE!!1one!! 99Skater99(Josh) - Although you're the biggest faggot in the world, <3. Lin - You were there when I needed to talk to someone. Exceptually about anal whore Ex-gfs. Sir pk p00n - <3 Tonypker13 - YOUZ BE TROLLIN!!! <3 Primadude - <3 Jc[Insert Random numbers here] - Although we fell out of touch, You were funny, and made lewk lulz. The soul - Although at times I feel you don't like me. That's fine. I still <3 you. The reaper X - nigger. nuff sed =D Newty - You are great to talk to, and funny too. The hunt - LOL Patrick - Although we got into a 'big' argument. we're still cool. pk3r john - i herd u wanted 2 b posted on da list so i posted on a list fur u. /facepalm. If I missed you. Post, I'll add you to the list.
Don't get me wrong, I'll still stop by and visit. Though I won't be very active, reason being is school, and other life issues. If you would like to know, please post.
Bye guys <3
P.s. I'm usually on the.dnsiskinky or Msn. If you wish to speak with me I'm there P.P.S sorry for posting this in the tutorial section >.>
